main event: Witnesses reported seeing a formation of eight bluish white UFOs flying in a V shape at high speed.
interesting points: The UFOs were observed flying at approximately 4000 miles per hour at an altitude of about 30 miles,The formation initially consisted of six saucers before two more joined them,The saucers were estimated to be about 100 feet in diameter,The objects disappeared into the horizon after being sighted for several seconds,No photographs or physical evidence were attached to the report.
sighted object: eight bluish white saucers in a V formation
